<h2 id="10">1. Important notes</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>This chapter provides you with important information about integrating the payment provider in plentymarkets.</p>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="20">1.1. Payment process</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>After confirming the order, the customer will be redirected to the ConCardis website. Here, they need to enter the data of the selected credit card. Once the customer has entered the data and confirmed the payment, they are directed back to your online store.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
